text: But mine’s turning out pretty good.
Those green eyes are the most important detail.
You’re not the only one drawing!
Cool!! Everything’s got a yellow hue!
What? You’re looking at me funny…
Mmm!! This one’s even more awesome!!
Hello, what are you staring at?
I have an even better idea!
I can’t wait to see what happens…
Woah… That’s a whole lot of color! Woah…
She’s officially lost her mind. My turn!!
Oh! Black and white bubble gum?
Wow! Never seen gum like this before!
Your back? I don’t get it.
It was an accident, I swear!
Well, why don’t you go first?
A potato? What’s exciting about this?
Oh no!! I got one too!
Not so funny now, is it?
Hmm… I’m gonna try something here.
It’s sure raw, it’s so hard!!
Gah!! I’m gonna give it one last stab…
You passed out! But look at your potato!!
WOAH!!! Check out all those awesome colors!!
Mmm, I could eat a million of these!
I wonder if they’re any good?
Well? Guess we’ll just hang out here.
You sure do have a lot of feathers.
What do you want us to do?
He’s not gonna hurt us, right?
What are we supposed to do now?
Well, it sure is pretty to look at.
But what will it taste like?
Ooh! This pizza is still frozen solid.
I can’t eat this. But I don’t have an oven.
But I do have a blow dryer!
Ooh! That’s not supposed to happen!!
Is it just me or does this pizza look way better?
Wonder what I got under here!
This doesn’t look anything like Lily’s!!
Should I try this blow dryer trick? Hm...
I have a better idea. B R B!
What is this place? She’s sleeping!
Mind if I borrow this for a sec?
This is gonna be really good!! Gotta go!!
Um…. How’d you find me here?
Ooh! That was a close one!
Mm… That was so worth getting in trouble with a witch!
And what do we have here?
Now this is what I call a good time!
But before I crack one open…
Let’s have a little fun with it!
And check out that finger work!
One two three four five six seven eight!!!
Ugh, I’ll just try to ignore her.
Looks like some fresh coffee beans!
Ahh. Just a few is all I need!
Dark roast is my favorite. Cheers!
Got stuff to do and people to see!!
C’mon guys, try to keep up!!
No prob! Now it’s time for my drink.
Mmm!! Mm-hm!! Hope there’s a bathroom nearby!
